<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一些事情永远不会改变。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>例如，老鼠永远害怕猫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当猫寻找食物的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一些老鼠很幸运，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一些就没那么幸运了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶酪城的老鼠们永远不会知道猫什么时候会出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也不会知道附近有多少只猫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对老鼠来说没有安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，老鼠们意识到他们得做点什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们决定开一个会议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请安静。”老鼠市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都知道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们和猫之间有一个很大的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们该怎么做？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只叫鲁克的老鼠举起手来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲁克，你有什么好主意吗？”市长问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以为猫设圈套！”鲁克激动地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不用奶酪做饵，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们做假老鼠。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有别的主意吗？”市长问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爱丽丝？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以毒死他们。”爱丽丝提议道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“趁他们在睡觉的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们把毒药放进他们的牛奶里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市长摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有别的主意吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠们开始议论纷纷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每只老鼠都有自己的主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一只充满智慧的老老鼠站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说话缓慢而镇定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我们听到一只猫在靠近，我们就躲起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们怎么能听到一只猫在靠近呢？”市长问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老老鼠停下想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以趁猫睡觉的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们的脖子上拴上铃铛。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当我们听到铃声，就知道一只猫在靠近。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的老鼠都站了起来，开始鼓掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真是个伟大的主意！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像所有的问题都解决了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是谁去给猫的脖子上拴铃铛？”一只小老鼠问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家停止了欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，老老鼠说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有些事情说比做容易。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>